Note that this documentation is related to Javasci v1. Please use Javasci v2.

Execute scilab :
--> cd SCI/modules/Javasci/examples/ihm
--> exec('builder.sce');

exit from scilab
make (from /modules/Javasci/examples/ihm)


export SCIDIR=<your current scilab path>
export SCI=<your current scilab path>
go to bin directory :
cd $SCIDIR/bin

export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$LD_LIBRARY_PATH:$SCIDIR/bin:.
(under HP unix platforms : export SHLIB_PATH=$SHLIB_PATH:$SCIDIR/bin:. )

export CLASSPATH=$CLASSPATH:$SCIDIR/bin:.

Could be recquired :
export TK_LIBRARY=$SCIDIR/modules/tclsci/tcl/tk8.4
export TCL_LIBRARY=$SCIDIR/modules/tclsci/tcl/tcl8.4



Under solaris platforms:
xrdb $SCIDIR/X11_defaults/Xscilab  (usually, xrdb can be found in /usr/openwin/bin/ directory)

java Test

Allan CORNET INRIA 2005
